{"tid":1468512,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[事態緊急] 明天要有心理準備，提防分化","createTime":"2019-08-13T19:00:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T01:04:52.000Z","uid":154808,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2a4d03a7d1df2a8643f05d3f365fd7886c77128a","tid":1468512,"uid":154808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:00:34.000Z","msg":"事關今日機場太多事情發生，先唔講邊個岩邊個錯，聽日大家一定要有心理準備會有好多話題，但係，各位手足聽到既時候<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">必須冷靜，唔好一劈頭就屌落去</span></strong></span>因為你一屌落去，就完全中左共狗詭計，成為分化撚。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地每一句說話都要小心，謹言，謹言，謹言</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n面對中立，淺藍，淺黃，我地絕對要比平時既心態更加沉着氣，慢慢解釋，可以參考曾健超以下既講法:<br />\n曾健超：「做法不完美，但可接受，要改善。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1466595\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1466595</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n兩個月抗爭，大家都行到呢一步，勇武手足保護左我地咁耐，勇武既進步大家有目共睹，依家要到和理非既進步:<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">心態進步</span></span></strong><br />\n聽日一定會有人咁講，我地咁做，同警犬有咩分別？(總會有呢班人，但唔好屌佢住！)但要慢慢解釋返，正所謂，對敵人仁慈，即係對自己殘忍，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你老母，你對住個冇底線既政權，警黑合作既軍政府仁慈？你對唔對得住死左嗰5個手足？對唔對得住比布袋彈射到眼盲既少女手足？對唔撚對得住比警犬告嗰600個手足呀？我屌你老母！！！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n亦有大愛既人士表示，對方只係政府既工具，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你老母，日本皇軍同納粹德軍夠係工具啦，屌你老母</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n好喇 大家心入面屌就算 <strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">千其，千其，千其唔好屌出口</span></span></strong>，一屌出口就變左分化撚<br />\n<br />\n大家同一陣綫，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">希望大家收起婦人之仁既心態</span></span></strong>，對住手足既行為一致表示<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不完美，但可接受</span></span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n最後，我地和理非既大愛係用係受傷既手足度，而唔係用係戰敗既警犬度，要分得清楚，保持清晰。<br />\n<br />\n最最後，亦都係重點，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">提防敵人分化時，要先防止自己分化</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港，時代革命，絕不割蓆！！！</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"7688e1a1296a21e71244d47b4e11d1f81621dfcc","tid":1468512,"uid":11515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:03:48.000Z","msg":"《香港機場說明書》全部同我入黎！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1468423\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1468423</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"696dc692f25fe2d3d7113dc4da543d1eca6312dc","tid":1468512,"uid":285481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:04:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/241gDjd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F241gDjd.jpg&h=24184809&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L3FpNcz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL3FpNcz.jpg&h=7d30142c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cDEudSz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcDEudSz.jpg&h=51c08fa7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RW360xA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRW360xA.jpg&h=82f5ceec&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eKyuYjf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeKyuYjf.jpg&h=abda31c4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SqmDREf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSqmDREf.jpg&h=86ba4115&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7jUudSB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7jUudSB.jpg&h=7ccf2950&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e8b12a8841197c02e88903fa8131317e251c3a71","tid":1468512,"uid":154808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T00:23:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"60ac10f3988eb7f5d1d489099b9e98d71d89ba5f","tid":1468512,"uid":154808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T00:42:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1b30d3f0d354a1e569944b1185aba2f36286b3e","tid":1468512,"uid":154808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:00:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4866e2749f1e24ace246ca99b497c200bfa40485","tid":1468512,"uid":294783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:04:52.000Z","msg":"黑警清機場洗撚申請禁制令。<br />\n<br />\n市民只係入去機場行下都話犯法咁咪拉鳩晒D香港人囉。<br />\n<br />\n由頭到尾都係因為政府強行立法，失敗後又唔認衰，又唔回應香港人訴求，高官們又玩失蹤，仲要同建制派一齊以警黑合作模式無差別打香港人。呢D全部都係香港政府一手造成。<br />\n<br />\n宜家黑警重傷咗咁多人，連記者同街坊都唔放過，仲要揾埋大陸武警去各區無差別打人，更開槍射頭，全冇人性。<br />\n<br />\n特首、高官、黑警、建制派、黑社會就算死十萬次都冇人會可憐，呢班臭蟲必須付全責。<br />\n<br />\n香港人係唔會向惡勢力低頭。<br />\n<br />\n手足們加油，大家萬事小心!<br />\n<br />\n一陣見!"}]}